// Semantic direction:
// ml_inferens runs trained neural network models on device using optimized backends.
// backend_npu targets Apple Neural Engine, Qualcomm Hexagon, or other neural processors.
// format_gguf is the GGUF format used by llama.cpp for quantized language models.
// format_safetensors is a safe, zero-copy tensor serialization format.
// tensor is the fundamental N-dimensional array; tensor_form is its [batch, seq, dim] dimensions.
// dtype_bf16 is bfloat16 — 8 exponent bits + 7 mantissa — used by modern LLMs for training.
// inferens_økt caches operator graphs and allocates buffers once; reuse for low latency.
// økt_varm_opp runs one forward pass to JIT-compile kernels before measuring latency.
// op_flash_oppmerksomhet is the memory-efficient attention algorithm (Flash Attention).
// kv_buffer caches previously computed key/value tensors for autoregressive text generation.
// kvant_int4 quantizes weights to 4 bits, reducing memory by 8× vs float32.
// kvant_kalibrering collects activation statistics on representative data before static quantization.
// bpe_tokenizer splits text into byte-pair subword tokens matching the model's token_vokabu.
// top_p_sampling (nucleus) samples from the smallest token set whose cumulative probability ≥ p.
// beam_søk maintains N candidate sequences and selects the highest-probability completion.
// nms_filter removes duplicate bounding boxes in objekt_deteksjon using non-maximum suppression.
// pipeline_batch groups multiple inputs for higher GPU throughput.

// Primitive flow:
// tekst_generering: tokenizer.kode(prompt) -> tensor([token_ids])
//   økt_kjør({inndata: token_tensor}) -> logits_tensor
//   top_p_sampling(logits, p=0.9) -> neste_token
//   legg til kv_buffer -> gjenta til stop_token | maks_lengde
//   tokenizer.dekode(token_ids) -> generert tekst
// bilde_klassifisering: last bilde -> bilde_forbehandling(resize, normalisering_bilde)
//   -> økt_kjør({inndata: bilde_tensor}) -> klassifiserings_logits
//   -> softmax -> topp-5 klasser + sannsynligheter
// objekt_deteksjon: økt_kjør -> boks_prediksjon + klasse_scores
//   -> nms_filter(iou_terskel=0.5) -> filtrerte bokser
// pipeline: forbehandlings_trinn -> inferens_trinn -> etterbehandlings_trinn
//   pipeline_batch(N=8): samle N inndata -> étt økt_kjør -> del utdata

// This defines the ML inference runtime: multi-backend tensor execution, quantization,
// LLM text generation with KV cache, image classification, object detection, and pipelines.
